          Latest Release
        </span>
        <span class="h-[2px] flex-1 bg-base-content/20 rounded-full"></span>
      </div>

      <div
        class="card glass-card max-w-sm mx-auto mt-24 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300 rounded-none"
